This paper discusses the need for automatic configuration tuning in Big Data systems, which involves optimizing the performance of multiple co-deployed systems. This topic is closely related to database systems (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), system and control theory (cs.SY), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
